discription: Rep some running legacy with every step you take while sporting the Nike Air Max Plus OG. Taking the best from Nike’s iconic sneakers in the past, these AM shoes nod to retro futurism. The upper blends synthetic leather and mesh to deliver flexible ease and proper breathability in one go.
